parameters.name: BX
parameters.description:
KSM X component of the magnetic-field in nT.                            
      X points from Saturn to the Sun.

parameters.name: BY
parameters.description:
KSM Y component of the magnetic-field in nT.                            
      Y is perpendicular to the magnetic dipole (Omega) and the               
      Saturn-Sun direction (Omega x X).

parameters.name: BZ
parameters.description:
KSM Z component of the magnetic-field in nT.                            
      Z is defined such that the X-Z plane contains Saturn's centered         
      magnetic dipole axis (M).

parameters.name: BTOTAL
parameters.description:
Average value of the full-resolution magnetic-field magnitudes          
      calculated over the averaging interval in nT. Note that this value      
      may differ slightly from the square root of the sum of the squares      
      of the averaged field components.

parameters.name: NPTS
parameters.description: Number of points in the average.
